  ;; Glossary:
  ;; - char-mode: All keystrokes except `exwm' global ones are passed to the
  ;;   application.
  ;; - line-mode:
  ;;
  ;; `exwm-input-global-keys' = {line,char}-mode; can also call `exwm-input-set-key'
  ;; `exwm-mode-map'          = line-mode
  ;; `???'                    = char-mode. Is there a mode-map for this?
